data.description: Sweet, well kept 2/2/1 CBS home in Spanish Lakes Fairways. Priced right for a quick sale. This community is a very friendly, active, community oriented, place to live. Nice 18 hole golf course, tennis court and pool.  Spanish Lakes offers many clubs, shuffle board, 2 pools with poolside cafe, pool tables, library, theater performances, clubhouse parties, and lots more. All amenities are included in lot fee.Lot fee is projected to Feb 1, 2017, may go up a few dollars or down depending on closing date.Special assesment is a yearly water fee only.
